thread.title: GLSEN Respect Awards presented at ceremony in Beverly Hills

author: Karen Butler
title: GLSEN Respect Awards presented at ceremony in Beverly Hills
text:
1 of 19 | License Photo BEVERLY HILLS, Calif., Oct. 24 (UPI) -- Jessica Biel , Zachary Quinto and Justin Timberlake were honored at the Gay, Lesbian and Straight Education Network Respect Awards ceremony this weekend.
Recording artist Timberlake and actress Biel -- who are married -- shared the Inspiration Award, while actor Quinto took home the Champion Award. The Student Advocate of the Year title was bestowed upon Mars Hallman.
Among the attendees at Friday night's gala in Beverly Hills were J.J. Abrams , Sasha Alexander, Morena Baccarin , Jason Collins , Dana Delany , Jeffrey Katzenberg , Shemar Moore, Jim Parsons and Julia Roberts .
